1. cloud contact center 
2. provide superior customer service at a lower cost


features of Amazon Connect:
  1. user administration
  2. Contact Control Panel(CCP)
  3. Contact flows
  4. Skill Based Routing
  5. Metrics and Reporting



  CCP : CCP is a client interface used by agents to handle customer contacts. Customers can use that comes from amazon
  connect or build the customer CCP using stream API.

  CRM : Customer Relationship Management, this approach manages the relationship and interactions with your
  customer and potential customer.

  Supervisor/Administrators:
    A person who overseas day to day operations of a contact center or part of a contact center in an 
    administrative function.

  Agent : 
  A person who handles inbound and outbound or both(blended) contacts of a contact center.
  
    
